<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Con" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Con,</orth> 1) to learn by heart: <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.2.102" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 2, 102</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.80.102" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.289" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 289</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.186" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 186</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.79" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 6, 79</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 1, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.1.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 1, 18</bibl>. <cit><quote>to c. by heart,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.98" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 98</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>without book,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 2.3.161" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 3, 161</bibl></cit>.*<cit><quote>by rote,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.98" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. IV, 3, 98</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) <emph>to c. thanks</emph> == to be thankful: <cit><quote>I c. him no thanks for it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.174" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 174</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thanks I must you c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.428" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 428</bibl></cit>.
